Confluence 4.0 introduces the ability for users to paste images from their clipboard. This was not implemented for Internet Explorer because [IE does not implement the HTML5 spec for thee Clipboard API| http://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/clipops/]. Once this is implemented by IE, we should be able to implement this feature.

This issue has been created to track the status of this.

