Internationalize "FAVOURITE_LABEL" in {{com.atlassian.confluence.labels.LabelManager}}.

At the moment it's hard coded as follow:
{code:title='com.atlassian.confluence.labels.LabelManager'}
    // the real spelling - let's use this by default for recording and looking up favourites
    String FAVOURITE_LABEL = "favourite";

    // the american spelling - let's use this on lookups only (in case people specify their own favourite labels manually)
    String FAVOURITE_LABEL_YANKEE = "favorite";
{code}

