The fix for CONF-17972 creates a slightly less-bad situation.  Previously, calling getById on PageManager with the id of a PersonalInformation (or any other non-Page) would return a Page object anyway and corrupt the cache until that object expired.  Now it just throws a ClassCastException straight away, which is still bad.

{noformat}

Caused by: java.lang.ClassCastException: com.atlassian.confluence.user.PersonalInformation cannot be cast to com.atlassian.confluence.pages.AbstractPage
        at com.atlassian.confluence.pages.persistence.dao.hibernate.HibernateAbstractPageDao.getAbstractPageById(HibernateAbstractPageDao.java:17)
{noformat}

