Multimedia file in [Multimedia macro|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF35/Embedding+Multimedia+Content] cannot be displayed on iPad mobile safari.

{+}{*}Workaround for this problem{*}{+}
Use <video> tag in \{html\} macro. Sample wiki markup is:
{noformat}
{html}
<video controls autoplay width="320" height="240">
  <source src="../download/attachments/12345678/sample.mov">
</video>
{html} 
{noformat}

